<FlowDocument xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
              ColumnWidth="400" FontSize="30" FontFamily="宋体"
              Foreground="Black">
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="36">定义：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">近整速算法，方法二，稍小于整千的两数相乘，可将一个乘数减另一个乘数凑成1000的补数，其差扩大1000倍，然后加上两个乘数凑成1000的补数相乘的积，所得结果即为所求之积。可用公式</Run>
        <LineBreak />
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="32">举例：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28">997×993=</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28" Foreground="Black">解答：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black"> 997×993</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=(997-7)×(993+7)+3×7</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=990×1000+21</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=990000+21</Run>
    </Paragraph>    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=990021</Run>
    </Paragraph>
</FlowDocument>